	   <tr><td colspan=2>To all you new wizards to the game heed this message.&nbsp;&nbsp;I have a hie wiz on Tarrew Marr but have recently stopped playing with him.  First of all pvp servers make the online gaming world much more interesting, not having to get permission to blast someone that annoys you is a good thing.  Also about the lvling thing crushbone is a good place for wizzy's to lvl until 12 or 13.  Don't lvl there if you're a dark elf wiz either isn't good for faction in Neriak.  After CB Oasis close to Freeport is a good place to lvl until 16 then you get invisibility and you can travel to lake of ill omen which is a good place to lvl until around 30.  If you're new to the game this will keep you busy for a while.  Also when you reach 24 you should start the staff of wheel quest which is long and arduous, get a great staff from it though.  Good luck and happy hunting.<br><br>P.S.  If some talk ass warrior tries to boss you around and tell you how to use your spells on a pvp server you can just let em have it and make him scream for his mommy.  <br>&nbsp;<br>That which we are we are, one equal temper of heroic hearts made weak by time and fate.&nbsp;&nbsp;To strive to seek to find and not to yield.  <br><br>Tennyson care of Sublimity</td></tr>
